[msg TUTORIAL_MSG01 [Disaster Shadows]]
[s]There are Shadows in the Metaverse called[n][clr 2]Disaster Shadows[clr 27].[n][w][e]

[msg TUTORIAL_MSG02 [Disaster Shadows]]
[s]Disaster Shadows will not act. However, [clr 2]when[n]attacked, they will counter and possibly perform[n]an additional attack[clr 27].[n][w][e]

[msg TUTORIAL_MSG03 [Disaster Shadows]]
[s]Disaster Shadows are tough. However, when defeated,[n][clr 2]they will drop an item[clr 27] and then explode, damaging[n]the surrounding Shadows.[n][w][e]

[msg TUTORIAL_MSG04 [Disaster Shadows]]
[s]The more damage they take when defeated,[n][clr 2]the more damage they inflict to surrounding[n]Shadows[clr 27]. Time your attacks well![n][w][e]

[msg TUTORIAL_MSG05 [Disaster Shadows]]
[s]However, if a Disaster Shadow is defeated by a[n]reflected attack or by Despair, it will not explode[n]and it will not drop any items.[n][w][e]

